{"tid":662023,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好似我咁，人越大越唔中意人類呢種動物","createTime":"2018-05-12T05:27:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T16:32:02.000Z","uid":122516,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0d0582c3b3d009d02adc5db00e07844b9f11269f","tid":662023,"uid":122516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:27:56.000Z","msg":"定係我太麻煩，嫌三嫌四<br />\n淨係覺得啲人好假，個個都無句真，<br />\n到講真又唔中意佢講真<br />\n寧願佢講假都唔想佢講真<br />\n<br />\n另外唔知點解，越大越想自己一個<br />\n追女唔想追，有機會就試，但試兩日又縮<br />\n覺得好攰，想抖，想靜，唔想人煩<br />\n覺得全世界都阻住自己咁<br />\n自己一手一腳比較舒服"},{"pid":"95b675ea077aa3505cc5c54d2d4109fdb69ac078","tid":662023,"uid":122516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:29:19.000Z","msg":"有女主動岩feel都唔想佢煩自己，點解會咁"},{"pid":"dac01ca1eb9fb1a4f39318a3048c57fb6e633c2f","tid":662023,"uid":122516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:35:19.000Z","msg":"？？"},{"pid":"1197a8c99cd51e4225034755c3662bb556397e90","tid":662023,"uid":69484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:38:59.000Z","msg":"唔好咁幼稚ok? <br />\n你只係逃避緊問題"},{"pid":"05ceab461a0a11ef6a78571bfbb00411514f0fa2","tid":662023,"uid":93792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"95b675ea077aa3505cc5c54d2d4109fdb69ac078","tid":662023,"uid":122516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:29:19.000Z","msg":"有女主動岩feel都唔想佢煩自己，點解會咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:40:33.000Z","msg":"首先要有女埋身...<br />\n<br />\n不過你講既野 我同意 覺得人人都有私心 好容易就對一個人冇好感"},{"pid":"4a96a6cd925066eaf230e35c4597787a8e9b74af","tid":662023,"uid":122516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1197a8c99cd51e4225034755c3662bb556397e90","tid":662023,"uid":69484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:38:59.000Z","msg":"唔好咁幼稚ok? <br />\n你只係逃避緊問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:45:18.000Z","msg":"下，但係我好enjoy <br />\n個問題係邊？"},{"pid":"614c14933601942fff8c187fd357496bb941eb48","tid":662023,"uid"